From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: slothfulchat <dev@slothfulchat.local>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 01:07:09 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 15/19] sticker picker: list animated .tgs stickers

misc_get_stickers only listed .png/.webp/.gif, so a saved Telegram animated
sticker (.tgs, now classified as Viewtype::Sticker) never appeared in the
composer sticker picker. Add .tgs to the accepted extensions.
---
 deltachat-jsonrpc/src/api.rs | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/deltachat-jsonrpc/src/api.rs b/deltachat-jsonrpc/src/api.rs
index bf1b29c..3b3de50 100644
--- a/deltachat-jsonrpc/src/api.rs
+++ b/deltachat-jsonrpc/src/api.rs
@@ -2612,6 +2612,7 @@ async fn misc_get_stickers(&self, account_id: u32) -> Result<HashMap<String, Vec
                 if sticker_name.ends_with(".png")
                     || sticker_name.ends_with(".webp")
                     || sticker_name.ends_with(".gif")
+                    || sticker_name.ends_with(".tgs")
                 {
                     sticker_paths.push(
                         sticker_entry
